item.title: Compiler
item.dc:creator: @PaulT PaulT
item.description:
@PaulT wrote:

nzkingnz:

wt does the compiler do??

A “Compiler” in this case is just a batch file that contains premade commands for compiling .java files. You can do the same thing using a command prompt, I suggest you do some reading here before continuing to work with java.

can u send me ur source plz?

You can find sources by looking in the downloads section of this forum or searching the forum.
